prompts.frontCover: A minimalist cartoon scene celebrating Jordan's birthday, centered on a pristine white background. In the middle, a stylized, sleek silver air fryer is depicted as a "Magical Machine," with whimsical sparkles and light rays emanating from it. Floating out of the air fryer are not french fries, but a charming cartoon fried egg with a bright yellow yolk and a fluffy mound of white rice, both with cute, happy faces. To the left, a friendly, simple robot character with a lightbulb icon on its chest, representing AI and problem-solving, is holding a small menu from a fancy restaurant. To the right of the air fryer, another small, friendly robot holds up a fork, ready to eat. The entire illustration uses clean lines, simple shapes, and a limited color palette of silver, yellow, white, and a touch of pastel blue for the robot accents. Centered below the illustration in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Jordan". The style is flat 2D vector art, perfect for a modern, humorous, and personalized greeting card.
